As a teenager, I progressed higher and higher in HP, slithered around that computer and started writing programs for it.
How Innovation Invents:
In several places, Jobs talks during the interview about how he invents new products while running.
In the early days of his career, when he set out to sell a couple of circuit boards, a customer asked him to assemble a whole computer for him.
